A man was found dead with numerous stab wounds on the N1 Highway in Meiringspark in Worcester. CAPE TOWN - A man has been found dead on the N1 Highway in Meiringspark in Worcester.Paramedics attended to the scene after receiving reports that a man had apparently been knocked over on Friday afternoon.Upon assessment, paramedics found the victim sustained numerous stab wounds.He was declared dead on the scene.ER24 s Russel Meiring says: Upon our arrival we found the man lying in the right lane of the highway in a small pool of blood. We immediately assessed him and found that he had sustained numerous fatal stab wounds and showed no signs of life. (Edited by Zamangwane Shange)